/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da12435e2f937c35fedbd5c90160f8e42d1ee619","tid":358396,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"我決定左今晚睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下佢點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07098e8c331ddd116d0fac0d08f333916e83e48b","tid":358396,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:32:56.000Z","msg":"可以試下去賣中藥既鋪頭買丁香，每日攞3-5g沖滾水當茶飲，飲幾個星期，聽人講話養胃同抑菌"},{"pid":"96cc42f403a47c4f764862129aacdcb052582f0b","tid":358396,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T13:02:44.000Z","msg":"F3 中過招 可以做到無限胃氣<br />\n多數係飲食問題 長期食難消化既野<br />\n食左8個月胃藥先好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e6fa98ca8a0d36d64d1a650ab637d3ace34855","tid":358396,"uid":25172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>F3 中過招 可以做到無限胃氣<br />\n多數係飲食問題 長期食難消化既野<br />\n食左8個月胃藥先好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我由細到大都無限胃氣..<br />\n由其前一晚飲好多酒 第朝會超多胃氣<br />\n平時就飲完一杯水都要gur下先會舒服。。<br />\n<br />\n我又係好少覺得肚餓.."},{"pid":"c9801b3f5d0cf40070ecb5bc4b857db44c534668","tid":358396,"uid":12111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T19:08:26.000Z","msg":"我仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n胃脹+胃氣多<br />\n唔好話食嘢飲多一兩啖即刻飽晒<br />\n睇左好多次醫生專科又排過<br />\n中醫就話慢性胃炎+腎炎<br />\n西醫就淨係話胃有啲發炎<br />\n但我已經成年幾冇正常食過一餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}